name: WhenisthenextSpaceXlaunch
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Lets you know when the next Space X launch is. It will tell once, the first time you install the skill, and then it will begin notifying you a few days before the launch.

Rocket ship icon made by Flat Icons from www.flaticon.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
